Package parsing.syntaxTree.expressions

BNF syntax token expression declarations. Classes in this package are used to represent the abstract syntax tree created when parsing a ucd file.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Expression
    General representation of an Expression of the BNF grammar.
